#### 3. Create IntegrationsCard Sub-component
**File**: `src/components/bento/IntegrationsCard.tsx` (new file)
**Purpose**: Extracted circuit board visualization from IntegrationsSection

This file will contain the full circuit board SVG implementation extracted from `IntegrationsSection.tsx`. Key adaptations:
- Remove the section wrapper and Container (BentoFeatures provides these)
- Remove the header text (will be part of the card content)
- Wrap in PlusCornerCard
- Adjust SVG viewBox/sizing to fit the 2x2 card dimensions
- Keep all circuit paths, signal animations, and icon foreignObjects

```tsx
